WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
 Find a place to attach the bias tape. Please mark your bias. 

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:24.000
 Please measure the perimeter of the cloth. 

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:42.000
 Mark the bias tape. 

00:00:51.126 --> 00:00:57.126
 Make a cut in the place where you put the mark. 

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:21.280
 Stack the bias tape so that the front side is on the inside. 

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:46.000
 Please spread the bias of the sewing tape 

00:01:49.705 --> 00:01:54.700
 Please fold the sewing allowance left and right. 

00:02:00.743 --> 00:02:05.740
 Align and cut the corners of the cloth. 

00:02:12.940 --> 00:02:25.940
 Since there is a thickness when sewed from the sewn place, please sew from a slightly offset place 

00:02:27.157 --> 00:02:32.160
 Please match the mark of the corner and the notch 

00:03:09.846 --> 00:03:14.850
 Please cut the extra thread at the end. 

00:03:17.591 --> 00:03:22.590
 Please fold the bias tape to the back side. 

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:49.840
 When you sew from the corner, the end falls into the hole and it becomes difficult to sew. Please sew from a distance from the corner of the cloth. 

00:03:54.363 --> 00:03:59.360
 Remove the waiting needle before the sewing needle. 

